<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="diet-n">diet <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'daɪət/    美 /'daɪət/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 日常饮食；日常食物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s important to have a <strong>balanced</strong>, <strong>healthy diet</strong>.
均衡、健康的日常饮食很重要。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Fat and salt are very important parts of a diet.
脂肪和盐是日常饮食中很重要的部分。</p><footer>2017 全国</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] (为健康或减肥的) 规定饮食</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-go-on-a-diet">be / go on a diet</h3>
<p>1.<strong>节食：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When I go on a diet, I eat only cucumbers, and that reduces my weight quickly. 
我节食的时候只吃黄瓜，迅速减轻了体重。</p></div></div>